\begin{frame}{Conclusion}
  \begin{itemize}
  \item Detect latent correlations in more than 2 datasets
  \item Statistics to detect correlations
  \item Proposed algorithm IMCCA with better performance in low-SNR, high dimension
    setting 
  \end{itemize}
